| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1928 — Recovery Inhibition (argonauts)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0b9fa3e3-8b4b-5ddc-b77a-1d77215e56e5"
